{"tid":1636393,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"心淡 身邊有沒有這種朋友","createTime":"2019-10-07T17:44:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T20:05:51.000Z","uid":274441,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"5ecc02615eb86d9953d6227a7d7fc628a245f91f","tid":1636393,"uid":274441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T17:44:23.000Z","msg":"‪有感而發‬ 心極淡<br />\n‪身邊有d朋友 狂屌黑警林鄭做既野‬<br />\n‪一叫佢地出去集會遊行 <br />\n就吱吱悟悟‬<br />\n六月到今日‪都吾知有冇出過去一次‬<br />\n‪出到來 一係就遲到 <br />\n一係連水都無 眼罩又無 毛巾又無 姐又無‬<br />\n‪你地天真認為自己神人咁勁吾會中到tear gas架wor ‬<br />\n‪點解一點保護自己既野都無‬<br />\n‪覺得人地幫你食晒就冇事嗎‬<br />\n吾係叫你地上前線啊<br />\n‪好啦 驚比人拉吾出來咁你繼續做和理非 <br />\n但又吾見佢地真係貼文宣 <br />\n開個Twitter都懶<br />\n仲搭黨鐵 <br />\n繼續係同溫層圍威喂<br />\n算啦 心都淡 係咪我太敏感？<br />\n因為我覺得好多人真係付出好多<br />\n點解你地明明有能力但吾做多一步"},{"pid":"1e855221c974a11c44cbb18fdc72beaa892ba994","tid":1636393,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T17:46:28.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"e31b09448819ad8ad7e5d9ce034e838ccb9122aa","tid":1636393,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T17:47:33.000Z","msg":"上緊連登既你 一個二個放低電話 暫時遠離連登！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1631560\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1631560</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4411aacdad5c8b2538170ad158c5aaa27988e221","tid":1636393,"uid":181581,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T17:48:20.000Z","msg":"唔 遮<br />\n算啦，有啲人覺得事不關己，係有冇責任感嘅問題，遠離呢啲朋友啦"},{"pid":"c4a31e01a064409d5b943cfc714b9c2ddc22eff8","tid":1636393,"uid":81569,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T17:48:27.000Z","msg":"信唔信連登都大把呢啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我知道有批人成日呃d朋友話自己有出去示威<br />\n事實上6月到宜家一次都無出過<br />\n純粹驚比朋友屌 先扮有示威<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ee9d2d809131c902c086f734c489cfe352792f9","tid":1636393,"uid":116343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T17:51:04.000Z","msg":"絕對唔係你太敏感 事實上仲有好多人自我陶醉<br />\n生活係溫層中  一日未燒到自己一日都唔會醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有時我都會好嬲想屌鳩佢地 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過凡事留一線 他日好相見 惟有少啲聯絡 繼續做自己認為對的事<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"883a395fb5f826c420afacae691cfe684d285391","tid":1636393,"uid":196227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T17:53:42.000Z","msg":"有出已經好好，唔好要求話咩物資<br />\n等佢慢慢進化<br />\n<br />\n利申身邊全部都係咁既人<br />\n多我一個唔多啦，正仆街黎<br />\n有時帶佢地出先慘，一早就要走覺得累"},{"pid":"f52033709c4c4f7129e59b3554d9efb630e1170a","tid":1636393,"uid":268591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T17:56:34.000Z","msg":"朋友係可以選擇的"},{"pid":"f7710261c44ad169dca07cd3f294f3ecfb321d88","tid":1636393,"uid":278527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T17:57:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ac389753e3f5df1c3b07f25cd56ac9305d3dc48","tid":1636393,"uid":266672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T17:58:30.000Z","msg":"我反而係叫身邊朋友都沒咩人出<br />\n<br />\n出親都係沒咩點帶裝 唔講以為係街坊look<br />\n<br />\n想搵個勇武陪我一齊上前線都沒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟住出親都話要早走 又話怕無車搭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20f8317086437b475c734fbe9fd333621e4e33ae","tid":1636393,"uid":57862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T17:59:15.000Z","msg":"民主free rider<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29b469411c4be16f71d2b7ecdb290ed41486ef9a","tid":1636393,"uid":279313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T18:02:57.000Z","msg":"有!朋友會自認懶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n怕危險616遊行都唔敢出<br />\nIG PO野俾朋友睇都好少<br />\n唔想dl tg,因為唔想再